285
00:20:22,550 --> 00:20:23,390
Mr. Xu.

286
00:20:23,990 --> 00:20:25,610
We've been searching for you all night.

287
00:20:25,680 --> 00:20:26,520
Where did you go?

288
00:20:27,600 --> 00:20:28,440
To avoid the rain

289
