291
00:20:32,920 --> 00:20:34,160
I've figured it out.

292
00:20:35,400 --> 00:20:36,510
Now, I'll go back to sleep

293
00:20:36,750 --> 00:20:37,840
and have a good meal.

294
00:20:38,510 --> 00:20:39,350
I'm leaving.

295
00:20:48,680 --> 00:20:49,680
By the way, Mr. Chu,

296
00:20:51,750 --> 00:20:53,310
I remembered the two lines.

297
00:20:53,440 --> 00:20:54,400
Do you still want them?

298
00:21:08,550 --> 00:21:09,400
Little one,

299
00:21:10,360 --> 00:21:11,200
eat more.

300
00:21:11,680 --> 00:21:13,440
Thank you, Ningyan.

301
00:21:18,270 --> 00:21:19,110
Sis,

302
00:21:19,550 --> 00:21:20,390
