Playing ring toss.

309
00:21:45,960 --> 00:21:47,200
Playing ring toss?

310
00:21:48,400 --> 00:21:49,240
Yeah.

311
00:21:57,510 --> 00:21:58,350
I'm full.

312
00:21:59,440 --> 00:22:00,280
Cijiu,

313
00:22:01,120 --> 00:22:02,190
I won't compete with you.

314
00:22:04,200 --> 00:22:05,040
Where are you going?

315
00:22:06,130 --> 00:22:07,400
Going to take a bath in my room.

316
00:22:07,470 --> 00:22:10,610
