you came as the autumn wind♪

317
00:22:10,610 --> 00:22:12,840
♪Turning my frown upside down♪

318
00:22:12,840 --> 00:22:15,670
♪With you, what is there to fear♪

319
00:22:15,990 --> 00:22:19,100
♪Let troubles come my way♪

320
00:22:21,200 --> 00:22:22,470
Eat some more.

321
00:22:24,330 --> 00:22:27,510
♪Though this world is bitterly cold♪

322
00:22:27,510 --> 00:22:29,640
♪I only wish for Xu's safety♪

323
00:22:29,640 --> 00:22:33,430
♪Neither joy nor sorrow lingers♪

324
00:22:33,730 --> 00:22:37,530
♪Petals fell; the fragrance lingers♪

325
00:22:37,860 --> 00:22:41,140
♪I pledge my life to you♪

326
00:22:42,640 --> 00:22:43,480
After eating,

327
00:22:43,550 --> 00:22:44,600
pack up your things,

328
00:22:44,710 --> 00:22:45,640
and leave the city.

329
00:22:47,160 --> 00:22:48,070
Listen to me.

330
00:22:49,570 --> 00:22:54,530
♪With you, I'll find peace♪

331
00:22:54,760 --> 00:22:57,950
♪Though this world is bitterly cold♪

332
00:22:57,950 --> 00:22:59,980
♪I only wish for Xu's safety♪

333
00:22:59,980 --> 00:23:04,240
♪Neither joy nor sorrow lingers♪

334
00:23:04,240 --> 00:23:08,350
♪Petals fell; the fragrance lingers♪

335
00:23:08,350 --> 00:23:14,550
♪I pledge my life to you♪

336
00:23:15,770 --> 00:23:19,440
♪To bloom brightly♪

337
00:23:27,030 --> 00:23:28,510
Report if necessary,

338
00:23:28,920 --> 00:23:30,960
or the court will be dismissed.

339
00:23:37,120 --> 00:23:37,960
Your Majesty,

340
00:23:38,510 --> 00:23:39,990
I have something to report.

341
00:23:41,680 --> 00:23:42,520
Speak.

342
00:23:43,680 --> 00:23:44,520
Your Majesty,

343
00:23:44,880 --> 00:23:46,960
Zheng Xinghuai, Commissioner of Chuzhou,

344
00:23:47,120 --> 00:23:48,470
committed suicide in prison

345
00:23:48,790 --> 00:23:49,710
at noon yesterday

346
00:23:50,230 --> 00:23:51,400
out of guilt.

347
00:23:54,270 --> 00:23:55,470
Out of guilt?

348
00:24:08,360 --> 00:24:09,990
What does everyone think?

349
00:24:10,680 --> 00:24:13,360
How should this case be concluded?

350
00:24:13,790 --> 00:24:14,630
Your Majesty,

351
00:24:14,920 --> 00:24:17,190
since Zheng Xinghuai has
committed suicide out of guilt,

352
00:24:17,200 --> 00:24:19,440
this case can be closed.

353
00:24:20,160 --> 00:24:22,360
Zheng Xinghuai, Commissioner of Chuzhou,

354
00:24:22,600 --> 00:24:23,790
from Zhangzhou,

355
00:24:23,790 --> 00:24:26,160
an A-II Presented Scholar
in Yuanjing Year 19,

356
00:24:26,360 --> 00:24:29,200
colluded with the Kui
to murder Duke Zhenbei

357
00:24:29,200 --> 00:24:31,640
and 380,000 commoners of Chuzhou.

358
00:24:31,640 --> 00:24:32,990
His crimes are heinous.

359
00:24:32,990 --> 00:24:34,510
Nine families of him shall be executed.

360
00:24:36,310 --> 00:24:37,920
Does he have any relatives left?

361
00:24:37,920 --> 00:24:39,470
This man is alone.

362
00:24:39,470 --> 00:24:41,070
His family is gone.

363
00:24:55,640 --> 00:24:56,880
Is this conclusion

364
00:24:57,640 --> 00:25:00,120
acceptable to everyone?

365
00:25:06,680 --> 00:25:08,360
Dismiss the court.

366
00:25:09,030 --> 00:25:11,120
Your Majesty, farewell.

367
00:25:27,880 --> 00:25:28,840
Who is it?

368
00:25:37,200 --> 00:25:38,310
Xu Qi'an.

369
00:25:38,790 --> 00:25:40,370
You cannot enter without being summoned.

370
00:25:40,710 --> 00:25:41,640
Mr. Xu,

371
00:25:41,640 --> 00:25:42,710
what brings you here?

372
00:25:57,200 --> 00:25:58,140
To seek justice.

373
00:26:00,750 --> 00:26:02,120
May Mr. Zheng rest in peace.

374
00:26:13,440 --> 00:26:14,280
Lord Wei.

375
00:26:32,630 --> 00:26:33,890
May Mr. Zheng rest in peace.

376
00:26:36,320 --> 00:26:37,630
May Mr. Zheng rest in peace.

377
00:26:43,440 --> 00:26:45,030
May Mr. Zheng rest in peace.

378
00:26:57,840 --> 00:26:59,200
May Mr. Zheng rest in peace.

379
00:27:06,120 --> 00:27:07,470
A wise strategist

380
00:27:08,680 --> 00:27:09,790
must know patience.

381
00:27:10,600 --> 00:27:11,920
Reckless courage,

382
00:27:12,310 --> 00:27:13,790
though it's satisfying for a moment,

383
00:27:15,400 --> 00:27:17,440
can cost you much more.

384
00:27:20,360 --> 00:27:21,640
The time is not right.

385
00:27:23,710 --> 00:27:24,550
Go back.

386
00:27:29,640 --> 00:27:30,880
Lord Wei and I

387
00:27:32,160 --> 00:27:33,550
are fundamentally different.

388
00:27:35,200 --> 00:27:36,840
You serve in the imperial court,

389
00:27:37,640 --> 00:27:38,880
overseeing the bigger picture.

390
00:27:40,710 --> 00:27:41,960
You're skilled in patience

391
00:27:42,680 --> 00:27:43,680
and adept at compromise.

392
00:27:44,680 --> 00:27:45,520
But I

393
00:27:47,840 --> 00:27:49,270
am just a Fighter.

394
00:27:50,310 --> 00:27:51,680
I cannot manage the bigger picture

395
00:27:52,230 --> 00:27:53,680
or do anything else.

396
00:27:56,440 --> 00:27:58,160
All I can do is strike decisively,

397
00:27:58,550 --> 00:27:59,920
clearing my conscience

398
00:28:01,600 --> 00:28:02,780
and staying true to my heart.

399
00:28:20,400 --> 00:28:22,270
Mr. Zheng gave me this before,

400
00:28:25,680 --> 00:28:26,880
but I believe

401
00:28:28,270 --> 00:28:29,440
it suits you better.

402
00:28:51,020 --> 00:28:53,940
(Take things slow.)

403
00:28:56,600 --> 00:28:57,840
State Duke Cao,

404
00:28:57,840 --> 00:28:59,960
shall we go to the Imperial Office
of Music tonight?

405
00:28:59,960 --> 00:29:01,400
After all these years in Chuzhou,

406
00:29:01,400 --> 00:29:03,880
I've forgotten
how pretty the music girls are.

407
00:29:03,880 --> 00:29:05,600
These days, don't leave your house.

408
00:29:05,600 --> 00:29:07,230
Just stay at your mansion.

409
00:29:10,070 --> 00:29:11,360
Xu Qi'an?

410
00:29:11,750 --> 00:29:12,590
Xu Qi'an,

411
00:29:13,270 --> 00:29:15,160
this is the Imperial Palace.

412
00:29:15,470 --> 00:29:16,920
What do you need a knife for?

413
00:29:17,070 --> 00:29:17,910
Xu Qi'an,

414
00:29:18,400 --> 00:29:20,880
do you know what crime you've committed

415
00:29:21,200 --> 00:29:23,990
by carrying a weapon
and trespassing into the Palace?

416
00:29:24,880 --> 00:29:25,790
Xu Qi'an,

417
00:29:25,920 --> 00:29:26,990
don't ruin yourself.

418
00:29:27,120 --> 00:29:28,270
You can't fight here.

419
00:29:28,270 --> 00:29:29,790
You can't afford the consequences.

420
00:29:30,360 --> 00:29:32,920
Is he Xu Qi'an, who investigated

421
00:29:33,070 --> 00:29:34,070
the Bloodshed Case?

422
00:29:34,550 --> 00:29:35,390
Yes,

423
00:29:35,550 --> 00:29:36,400
it's him.

424
00:29:36,600 --> 00:29:37,550
Que Yongxiu,

425
00:29:38,070 --> 00:29:39,030
State Duke Cao,

426
00:29:39,710 --> 00:29:40,710
come here.

427
00:29:41,880 --> 00:29:43,880
If I kill him here,

428
00:29:44,400 --> 00:29:45,880
will His Majesty blame me?

429
00:29:46,680 --> 00:29:49,200
His cultivation is too great
to be underestimated.

430
00:29:56,510 --> 00:29:59,230
I am the one you're looking for.

431
00:30:00,310 --> 00:30:01,310
What do you want to do?

432
00:30:03,470 --> 00:30:04,400
Lord Wei,

433
00:30:04,840 --> 00:30:06,880
your teaching skills are insufficient.

434
00:30:07,070 --> 00:30:09,070
Look at this lawless young man.

435
00:30:09,310 --> 00:30:11,440
How dare he carry a weapon
in the Palace?

436
00:30:12,120 --> 00:30:13,400
If you can't teach him,

437
00:30:13,990 --> 00:30:15,920
I'll teach him for you.

438
00:30:17,700 --> 00:30:18,540
(Restraining Spell)

439
00:30:29,880 --> 00:30:31,310
Someone broke into the Palace!

440
00:30:31,440 --> 00:30:33,040
Close the gates
and protect His Majesty!

441
00:30:33,250 --> 00:30:34,170
Let's go.

442
00:30:36,070 --> 00:30:36,910
Don't go!

443
00:30:37,310 --> 00:30:39,030
Come back! Don't leave!

444
00:30:39,270 --> 00:30:40,110
Lord Wei,

445
00:30:40,440 --> 00:30:41,840
as a fellow official,

446
00:30:42,160 --> 00:30:43,440
you can't ignore this.

447
00:30:45,760 --> 00:30:46,640
Xu Qi'an,

448
00:30:46,640 --> 00:30:47,790
don't come over! Calm down!

449
00:30:48,070 --> 00:30:48,910
Xu Qi'an!

450
00:30:53,200 --> 00:30:54,120
Imperial Guards.

451
00:30:54,120 --> 00:30:55,330
Where are the Imperial Guards?

452
00:30:55,330 --> 00:30:56,440
Take him down!

453
00:30:56,440 --> 00:30:58,660
The Imperial Guards
only follow His Majesty's orders.

454
00:30:58,790 --> 00:30:59,630
Turn around.

455
00:31:00,200 --> 00:31:01,040
Imperial Guards,

456
00:31:01,310 --> 00:31:02,440
you can't ignore this!

457
00:31:04,790 --> 00:31:05,710
Xu Qi'an, you...

458
00:31:05,710 --> 00:31:06,710
Don't, Mr. Xu.

459
00:31:07,230 --> 00:31:08,070
Mr. Xu.

460
00:31:10,230 --> 00:31:12,000
Lord Wei!

461
00:31:13,030 --> 00:31:14,750
Lord Wei!

462
00:31:14,750 --> 00:31:15,640
Help me!

463
00:31:15,990 --> 00:31:16,880
Help me!

464
00:31:18,230 --> 00:31:19,550
Xu Qi'an, stop!

465
00:31:19,550 --> 00:31:21,440
I am the State Duke of Protection!

466
00:31:35,200 --> 00:31:36,400
Lord Wei!

467
00:31:36,400 --> 00:31:38,750
- Help me!
- Lord Wei, help me!

468
00:31:39,790 --> 00:31:41,120
Where are the Imperial Guards?

469
00:31:41,120 --> 00:31:41,960
Imperial Guards!

470
00:31:42,600 --> 00:31:43,790
Lord Wei!

471
00:31:52,440 --> 00:31:53,550
They're just paying

472
00:31:53,990 --> 00:31:54,920
for their grave sins.

473
00:31:55,440 --> 00:31:56,550
Help me!

474
00:32:16,640 --> 00:32:17,510
Your Majesty!

475
00:32:17,750 --> 00:32:18,590
Your Majesty!

476
00:32:19,070 --> 00:32:20,070
Your Majesty!

477
00:32:20,230 --> 00:32:21,310
This is terrible!

478
00:32:21,550 --> 00:32:23,030
Xu Qi'an captured State Duke Cao

479
00:32:23,160 --> 00:32:25,370
and the State Duke of Protection
at the Meridian Gate.

480
00:32:25,470 --> 00:32:26,600
He even talked

481
00:32:26,990 --> 00:32:28,030
about killing them!

482
00:32:29,230 --> 00:32:31,030
Is he planning to rebel?

483
00:32:31,710 --> 00:32:33,310
How are things with State Duke Cao

484
00:32:33,550 --> 00:32:35,010
and the State Duke of Protection now?

485
00:32:35,020 --> 00:32:36,610
They've been taken out of the Palace.

486
00:32:40,440 --> 00:32:41,360
Hurry and stop him!

487
00:32:42,070 --> 00:32:43,030
If anyone resists,

488
00:32:43,070 --> 00:32:44,550
kill them on the spot!

489
00:32:44,640 --> 00:32:45,480
Yes!

490
00:32:46,200 --> 00:32:47,840
How dare he defy me!

491
00:32:51,030 --> 00:32:52,030
How rebellious!

492
00:32:52,960 --> 00:32:55,400
How rebellious!

493
00:32:56,550 --> 00:32:57,390
Mr. Xu,

494
00:32:57,790 --> 00:32:58,630
how about

495
00:32:58,800 --> 00:33:00,930
I treat you to a bowl of plain noodles?

496
00:33:02,160 --> 00:33:03,970
I'm over fifty,

497
00:33:04,640 --> 00:33:06,120
reaching the age of knowing my fate.

498
00:33:07,370 --> 00:33:09,120
I've never had grand ambitions.

499
00:33:09,960 --> 00:33:12,230
I just wanted to take care of my mother,

500
00:33:12,510 --> 00:33:14,030
spend time with my kids and grandkids,

501
00:33:14,360 --> 00:33:16,440
and keep Chuzhou peaceful.

502
00:33:18,270 --> 00:33:19,990
But overnight,

503
00:33:21,840 --> 00:33:23,600
Chuzhou was lost,

504
00:33:24,890 --> 00:33:25,830
and those people

505
00:33:26,310 --> 00:33:27,960
were all dead.

506
00:33:28,640 --> 00:33:30,710
Maybe Lord Wei is right

507
00:33:31,790 --> 00:33:33,160
about taking things slow.

508
00:33:34,230 --> 00:33:35,270
But

509
00:33:35,640 --> 00:33:37,270
I can't stop.

510
00:33:59,230 --> 00:34:00,070
Chu Yuanzhen,

511
00:34:00,360 --> 00:34:01,470
are you planning to rebel

512
00:34:01,680 --> 00:34:02,850
and become a wanted criminal?

513
00:34:11,990 --> 00:34:13,120
I spent ten years

514
00:34:14,360 --> 00:34:15,510
sharpening my sword.

515
00:34:17,070 --> 00:34:18,230
Its edge

516
00:34:19,440 --> 00:34:20,960
has never been tested.

517
00:34:23,360 --> 00:34:24,470
Today,

518
00:34:26,470 --> 00:34:28,070
it's shown to the world.

519
00:34:30,670 --> 00:34:32,030
Who

520
00:34:34,720 --> 00:34:35,560
needs

521
00:34:36,400 --> 00:34:37,360
help

522
00:34:37,880 --> 00:34:38,720
with grievances?

523
00:34:53,240 --> 00:34:54,470
His Majesty has ordered

524
00:34:54,470 --> 00:34:55,920
that anyone who resists

525
00:34:55,920 --> 00:34:57,030
be killed on the spot.

526
00:34:57,030 --> 00:34:58,400
Try me!

527
00:35:03,670 --> 00:35:04,590
This time,

528
00:35:05,470 --> 00:35:07,400
we've really stirred up a hornet's nest.

529
00:35:07,400 --> 00:35:08,840
Leave if you're afraid.

530
00:35:10,190 --> 00:35:11,550
I'm here.

531
00:35:17,510 --> 00:35:18,550
How could I

532
00:35:19,070 --> 00:35:20,800
not be part of this?

533
00:35:45,760 --> 00:35:46,960
Isn't this Mr. Xu?

534
00:35:46,960 --> 00:35:47,800
Yeah.

535
00:35:48,150 --> 00:35:49,280
Who are those two?

536
00:35:49,510 --> 00:35:50,350
The one-eyed man is

537
00:35:50,470 --> 00:35:52,320
Que Yongxiu, State Duke of Protection.

538
00:35:52,590 --> 00:35:53,430
Look.

539
00:35:53,510 --> 00:35:54,540
With so many people here,

540
00:35:55,190 --> 00:35:56,510
your death will be worth it.

541
00:35:57,590 --> 00:36:00,360
He accused Zheng Xinghuai,
Commissioner of Chuzhou,

542
00:36:00,360 --> 00:36:03,320
of colluding with the Kui
to murder Duke Zhenbei.

543
00:36:03,990 --> 00:36:05,760
Yeah, how could they do this?

544
00:36:06,110 --> 00:36:07,590
What's happening?

545
00:36:07,590 --> 00:36:10,190
It's probably about the Chuzhou Case.

546
00:36:10,800 --> 00:36:12,630
I'm a Tier I Duke,

547
00:36:12,630 --> 00:36:15,240
a descendant of a founding hero.

548
00:36:16,030 --> 00:36:17,630
If you kill me,

549
00:36:17,720 --> 00:36:21,150
you won't have a place
in the Dafeng anymore.

550
00:36:21,760 --> 00:36:23,240
When I meet His Majesty,

551
00:36:23,240 --> 00:36:25,240
I will surely beg him

552
00:36:25,470 --> 00:36:27,470
to forgive you.

553
00:36:28,320 --> 00:36:29,320
Mr. Xu,

554
00:36:29,960 --> 00:36:31,960
please spare me.

555
00:36:32,760 --> 00:36:35,070
It was Duke Zhenbei
and the State Duke of Protection.

556
00:36:35,550 --> 00:36:37,800
They slaughtered the city.

557
00:36:37,800 --> 00:36:38,840
They did it.

558
00:36:38,840 --> 00:36:40,030
It has nothing to do with me!

559
00:36:40,030 --> 00:36:42,110
- Nonsense!
- You're the one talking nonsense!

560
00:36:42,110 --> 00:36:43,190
You weren't in the capital.

561
00:36:43,190 --> 00:36:44,720
You don't know him.

562
00:36:44,720 --> 00:36:45,560
He's a madman.

563
00:36:45,570 --> 00:36:47,190
He really will kill us.

564
00:36:47,670 --> 00:36:49,720
Please don't!

565
00:36:51,240 --> 00:36:52,080
Speak louder.

566
00:36:52,840 --> 00:36:54,240
Tell the people.

567
00:36:54,630 --> 00:36:55,470
Who was it

568
00:36:55,550 --> 00:36:56,630
that massacred Chuzhou?

569
00:36:59,880 --> 00:37:01,280
It was Duke Zhenbei

570
00:37:01,440 --> 00:37:04,670
and the State Duke of Protection
who massacred the city!

571
00:37:05,760 --> 00:37:07,030
It was them!

572
00:37:07,590 --> 00:37:08,880
Who would've thought of that?

573
00:37:09,990 --> 00:37:10,830
That's not enough.

574
00:37:12,440 --> 00:37:13,840
Zheng Xinghuai...

575
00:37:14,840 --> 00:37:16,150
